-------------------------------------------------------------------------

#stream editor (sed) - searching, find and replace, insertion or deletion

* sed 's/murthi/anusha/' file (replace 1st word with anusha)

s - substring

/ - delimiter

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Nth Replacement

* sed 's/murthi/anusha/2' file (replace 2nd word with anusha)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

* sed 's/unix/linux/g' file (replace all, g-global)

* sed 's/unix/linux/3g' file (replace all from 3rd)

* sed '3 s/unix/linux/' file (replace only in 3rd line)

* sed '1,3 s/unix/linux/' file (replace from 1st line to 3rd)

* sed '5d' file (delete 5th line)

* sed '$d' file (delete last line)

* sed '3,6d'file (delete from 3rd line to 6th)

* sed '12,$d' file (delete from 12th line to last)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------